comments: Waiters (LAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Morris (DEN) after the release that does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally on his jump shot attempt.

After the pick, Kuzma (LAL) and Plumlee (DEN) engage and disengage as Plumlee rolls to the basket.

comments: Dozier's (DEN) hand is out of bounds when his arm makes contact with the ball.
